text: Bulanov () is a Russian masculine surname, its feminine counterpart is Bulanova. It may refer to *Aleksandr Bulanov (born 1989), Russian shot putter *Igor Bulanov (born 1963), Russian footballer *Maria Bulanova (born 1998), Russian bowler *Tatiana Bulanova (born 1969), Russian singer *Vyacheslav Bulanov (born 1970), Russian ice hockey referee Category:Russian-language surnames
title: Bulanov
